			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p8354" cert="high">Laetus</persName><note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2"><persName ref="p8354" cert="high">Georg Frölich</persName>.</note> scripsit<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3">Siehe <ref target="file12621">Nr. 2574</ref>,37-42 (vom 8. oder 9. September).</note> exercitum nostrorum <placeName ref="l231" cert="high">Ingolstadio</placeName> relicto <placeName ref="l119" cert="high">Werdam</placeName><note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4"><placeName ref="l119" cert="high">Donauwörth</placeName>.</note> contendisse.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Haec ultima sunt, quae habemus.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nos ergo hic valde solliciti sumus, ne quid nostri negligant.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vaferrimus est hostis, potens et exercitus.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Oberrant nostri subinde.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sumptus crescunt.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si ita oberrare, nihil proficere perrexerint, quis tandem sumptus maximos et plus quam regios suppeditabit?</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed in his cogitationibus consolatur me egregie divina providentia, gratia et misericordia causaeque bonitas, et quod video suis nunquam defuisse dominum,<note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5">Vgl. <cit type="bible"><ref>Neh 9, 17. 19. 31</ref></cit>; <cit type="bible"><ref>Ps 37 (Vulg. 36), 28</ref></cit>; <cit type="bible"><ref>94 (Vulg. 93), 14</ref></cit>; <cit type="bible"><ref>Jes 41, 17</ref></cit>; <cit type="bible"><ref>Hebr 13, 5</ref></cit>.</note> impios conatus, artes, potentiam et ferociam semper fregisse<note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6">Vgl. <cit type="bible"><ref>1Sam 2, 9</ref></cit>; <cit type="bible"><ref>Hi 5, 12</ref></cit>; <cit type="bible"><ref>Ps 37 (Vulg. 36), 17</ref></cit>; <cit type="bible"><ref>145 (Vulg. 144), 20</ref></cit>; <cit type="bible"><ref>Jes 8, 10</ref></cit>.</note>.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quod ut nunc quoque faciat, sedulo oremus, aut, si illi visum est nostram fidem exercere et probare nos, ut constantiam in fide et patientiam in tormentis conferat<note xml:id="fn7" type="footnote" n="7">Vgl. <cit type="bible"><ref>Jakl, 3</ref></cit>; <cit type="bible"><ref>1Petr 1, 7</ref></cit>.</note>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
			<div xml:id="div2" corresp="regest2">
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Valeas optime cum universa familia et symmistis charis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Ohne Adresse.]</note>
				</p>
			</div>
